name: Nendoroid Nino Nakano: Wedding Dress Ver.
description:
"With love, you really have to be on the offensive."

From the anime special "The Quintessential Quintuplets ∽" comes a Nendoroid of Nino Nakano in her wedding dress outfit!

Face plates:


Blushing face
Winking face


Optional parts:


Bouquet
Petal shower background sheet
Other optional parts for different poses.

details.value: Nendoroid Nino Nakano: Wedding Dress Ver.
Painted plastic non-scale articulated figure with stand included. Approximately 100mm in height.
